<br>
Realize you do not always need an arrow to pull mobs, especially the closer you make it to 60.  You can use your aggro radius to pull instead of an arrow, and that can help reduce the number of adds you get.  <br>
<br>
Warriors, in many situations, often make the best pullers in the game.  Those warriors that strive to be pullers in situations such as hateplane and HoT, are usually better than monks at pulling those areas.  The reason, it has to do with NOT having Feign Death.  We learn to do it without making any mistakes, when monks care not because of their get-out-of-death-free card.<br>
